                <div class="j-num">3</div>
                <div class="j-card">
                    <h3>Ship With Confidence</h3>
                    <p>Every PR gets a full QA review, test results, and Playwright code — before it merges. Your team iterates on <strong>product feedback</strong>, not bug reports.</p>
